name: #1 REMORSE
description:
Shunned to the weeping hollows, Lord Remorse hunted his prey by sensing fear. When the scent of dread neared his abandoned dwelling, he bewitched the hunters seeking sanctuary with the allure of a new haven. 

Drawing them deeper into the dark hound dungeons. Their flesh ripped and bodies were strewn, the hunters continued to weep, and the Lord revealed in the reek of Remorse.
